thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by SB

author: SB
title: SB
text:
We chose the budget option for our 3 week holiday with our 15-month old daughter. The Nissan Tiida we were provided with drove well, was very efficient and spacious. It was great that a car seat was provided for free (although for babies/toddlers more modern, better padded seats would be better).
We were pleased with the service we received from Omega. Picking up and returning the car were both quick and easy and we had were transferred immediately to the airport on bringing the car back.
